# Goal
bonbon_msgs/ActuationGesture[] gestures
bool loop                  # repeat sequence
int32 loop_count           # 0 = loop forever
---
# Result
bool success
int32 gestures_completed
string[] failed_gestures
string error_message
---
# Feedback
int32 current_gesture_index
string current_gesture_name
float32 progress_pct
bonbon_msgs/ActuationStatus current_status
